Maintainer: Belay Birlie Yimer <belaybirlie.yimer@manchester.ac.uk>
Description: The R package drugprepCPRD prepares the prescription data from CPRD in to analysis ready format with start and stop date for each prescription per individual. Based on Pye et al. (2018) <https://doi.org/10.1002/pds.4440>
